SVGCircleElementCy.summary: The cy read-only property of the interface reflects the {{SVGAttr("cy")}} attribute of a {{SVGElement("circle")}} element and by that defines the y-coordinate of the circle's center.

remarks.para: If unspecified, the effect is as if the value is set to 0.

SVGCircleElementCy.value: An representing the y-coordinate of the circle's center.
